Investment Canada said it has allowed theindirect takeover of Holt, Rinehart and Winston Canada Ltd.,W.B. Saunders Co of Canada Ltd and Les Editions HRW Ltd byHarcourt Brace Jovanovich Canada Inc.    The government agency said, however, Harcourt Canada hasagreed to sell control of the firms to Canadian interestswithin two years.    Harcourt Canada's U.S. parent, Harcourt Brace JovanovichInc &lt;HBJ>, indirectly acquired the Canadian book publishingcompanies when it purchased Holt Rinehart and Winston from CBSInc &lt;CBS> last October.            Reuter&#3;